Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.85,0:01:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藤田  藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天助我也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今早出現在山麓駐紮處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.62,0:02:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正飛車趕來我們這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.73,0:02:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就會抵達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已不是以前的緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼短的時間\N他究竟做了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.12,0:02:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是傳說中的緋村劍心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.73,0:02:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐馬車來訪\N好像大官駕到的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他已決定重回江湖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.84,0:02:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十五話 煉獄戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.08,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.69,0:03:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你抓來的張十刀透露的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.52,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今早我們抓到\N另一個志志雄的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.73,0:03:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還讓我們看了他們準備\N火燒京都的計劃信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.73,0:03:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們決定今晚\N十一時五十九分開始行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是有趣極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.71,0:03:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論志志雄有多厲害\N但一定寡不敵眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.75,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此他們必需採取\N突擊和暗殺的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.85,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照理說像張十刀\N口風這麼緊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.42,0:03:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會  這麼輕易就此招供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼他會那麼快\N就將計劃告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼高見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.90,0:03:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們將火燒京都的秘密\N洩露給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是別有居心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.71,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位  行動就要開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.11,0:04:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們沒有必要再繼續躲藏此處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要藉著我們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喚醒沉睡已久的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.63,0:04:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂別有居心是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.66,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄的目的\N不外是復仇和竊國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.50,0:04:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他還有其他\N我們不知道的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟有什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.85,0:04:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川慶喜將軍\N由大阪坐船逃回江戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.85,0:04:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官軍才得以大獲全勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許志志雄這次\N也想利用這個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.59,0:04:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來個措手不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.00,0:04:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都大火只是\N他們作戰的第一階段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.47,0:05:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘船由海上炮擊東京\N才是他們真正的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.77,0:05:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火燒京都只是\N分散我們的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪那麼簡單\N就洩露情報給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.32,0:05:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實他們的目標\N是在首善之都東京
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點就被他們騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們現在一定已經出發了\N我們要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又想放我鴿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一次不會讓你如願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助  你怎麼在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼在這裏問你緋村劍心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂越幫越忙真是一點也沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.35,0:05:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.85,0:05:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間緊迫了  還不快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到大阪用走的嗎  笨蛋坐馬車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙真是嚕嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.26,0:06:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬車快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直奔大阪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.58,0:06:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別囉嗦  安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.99,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.25,0:06:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都現有五千警力\N人數是志志雄的數十倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是為防止京都起火\N而部署的人力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今早的密報信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那封計劃信是不是有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.57,0:06:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們派了幾乎\N全部的警力在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只為了阻止京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是從以前到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.81,0:06:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都一直是志志雄的反攻重鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人力本來就都聚集在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.10,0:07:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事  阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對不對  是幫主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.21,0:07:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機關鎗一把要多少錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.25,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說機關鎗是火力強大的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.39,0:07:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打敗志志雄\N就得添購這種裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.53,0:07:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許機關鎗是\N攻擊力強大的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你們真正的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.97,0:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許並非是這些武器\N所能替代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你千萬別不看自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真正的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.55,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了\N我相信我們會成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.39,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你  小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是劍心寫來的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.47,0:08:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天路上那麼多警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.81,0:08:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火燒京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一團亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.61,0:08:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是今天才開始一團亂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了  阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以幫主命令你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定要阻止火燒京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快以飛鴿傳書聯絡京都那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,近江女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家換好衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要採取行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥  我們也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.85,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我們在東京和蒼紫決鬥時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.22,0:09:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾立誓與御庭幫  誓不兩立的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間了  大家動作快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在人手幾乎全分配在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.57,0:09:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大阪方面不可能再增加人手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.87,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且無論馬車多快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到大阪一定已超過\N十二點以後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要再找志志雄的下落\N一定會來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦  緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.78,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這囉嗦  就會有辦法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使東京被志志雄炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.39,0:09:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不會那麼簡單就給打爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們既然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就和他們直接上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你敢再打一次試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這笨蛋\N你不講話沒人把你當啞巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.81,0:10:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助\N你不要小看志志雄的破壞力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.85,0:10:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘉永六年浦賀沖就是藉著艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才能成為開國天皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從幕府末年到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.86,0:10:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東京人民一直\N活在不安恐懼之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.86,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使到今天\N仍禁不起一點的傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.50,0:10:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,些許的炮擊\N就會造成東京的大混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.94,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以現在政府的力量\N根本毫無招架的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,東京馬上會成為無法地帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.62,0:10:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此  只要能攔截志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.56,0:10:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能阻止這一切發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再遲就來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.48,0:11:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我的經驗\N志志雄行動的條件有二個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.69,0:11:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個是利用夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.69,0:11:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個就是利用混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.70,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前志志雄就是利用\N這兩個方法來達成他的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這傢伙一定\N也是想利用這個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.27,0:11:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混水摸魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.54,0:11:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想這傢伙的船一定是\N混在靠岸的民家漁船內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.96,0:12:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄先生\N我們這次的計劃很周詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.03,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心到現在\N都沒發現我們的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使他們現在發現也來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.13,0:12:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許現在他們已經知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了  由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.41,0:12:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道這次的計劃很秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.58,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是究竟這艘船\N是什麼樣子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.22,0:12:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是想看看這艘船的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你心裏在想什麼  我全知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.76,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然早晚都要看到\N我現在就帶你去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們最後的王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把它叫做煉獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.65,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得怎樣  由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治  幾點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十一點二十二分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離火燒京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.33,0:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煉獄出航
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.40,0:13:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有三十七分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.48,0:13:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間到了  火怎麼還沒起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.42,0:13:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耐心一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.66,0:13:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市內大批警力部署\N我們人手遭遇阻攔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼遇到這種情況  真傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.77,0:13:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法  必需變更作戰計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們快去放火  我去解決他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.14,0:14:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的任務\N只是暗殺高官要員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.05,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不需要殺死警官和人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.82,0:14:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大火一燒\N所有的人都是死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別想阻攔我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.86,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來我也不必顧慮太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.43,0:14:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯我啊我我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這笨蛋別跟來  笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.22,0:14:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓這些傢伙看看\N我們警察的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀隊  前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了  他們人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.73,0:15:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你們這些膽小鬼往哪裏逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.78,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我大鐮刀的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.49,0:15:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我蝙也在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以幫你們掩護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還不快進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.14,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕  堅守到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.93,0:16:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了\N我們趁現在全面進攻警備隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.61,0:16:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位  找到放火的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.78,0:16:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.22,0:16:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰  究竟想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操  不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是御庭幫的新幫主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.87,0:16:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人都被我們解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.71,0:16:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.14,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家還要保持高度警戒才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位  我們就照原定計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做好防火和防衛準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.05,0:16:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.85,0:16:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫主你也小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.36,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.19,0:17:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.13,0:17:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到御庭幫這麼受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.27,0:17:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是出人意料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.14,0:17:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都是老翁十年來努力的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.34,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭幫的實力  還是很堅強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他們勇敢的樣子就可以知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.35,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭幫將來一定會有所作為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.19,0:17:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了  大家解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰 彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.57,0:17:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來就是你這個小鬼在搞亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.39,0:18:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼慢\N京都方面究竟在搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.83,0:18:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在火還沒放起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方有五千警力\N多少都得花點功夫收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過也太慢了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.37,0:18:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必太著急  所謂欲速則不達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.35,0:18:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是志志雄\N能說出這麼有哲理的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.92,0:18:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然說是作戰\N但想到故居被火燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心中仍有些許不捨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.53,0:18:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心還是太軟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必再為莫須有的理由感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.66,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們快搭我們的戰艦出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.90,0:18:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都大火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是我們勝利的焰火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和他的決鬥還未一決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想到這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不禁令人感到遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火點起來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.16,0:19:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒  有一輛超快速的馬車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄的船在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏  那艘木船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.84,0:19:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個煙就是準備出航的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.85,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為是什麼大軍艦\N沒想到是艘破船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.92,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,載我都載不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些傢伙  在這幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄先生  我們被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.90,0:20:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧曾是最親近的戰友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.11,0:20:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼瞭解我的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.58,0:20:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道現在就要提前決鬥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.55,0:20:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在時間緊迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.22,0:20:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間和這些人攪和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,方治  全體進入艦內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.36,0:20:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們阻擋不了我的\N你們等著看我勝利吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.64,0:20:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們必須潛水靠近船身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後從船底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.58,0:20:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要挖洞不能用刀劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.25,0:20:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來東京時 身上帶了炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.42,0:20:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是不用點火的最新型炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.89,0:21:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個囉嗦的男人\N到底對我哪裏不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.77,0:21:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使不用點火\N在海裏炸彈也無法引爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.87,0:21:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈在海裏 是起不了作用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.71,0:21:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就在這乖乖的\N等大阪警備隊來就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.28,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好別輕舉妄動
